comments: Green (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding Ayton (PHX).
Poole (GSW) briefly applies a slight hand to Paul's (PHX) front during the drive before Paul brushes it away, and marginal contact occurs.
Green (GSW) applies his left hand to Bridges' (PHX) side and grabs his jersey during the screen, which affects Bridges' ability to defend the drive by Poole (GSW).
Booker (PHX) grabs the left arm of Poole (GSW) on the drive and affects his SQBR.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly grasps Paul's (PHX) jersey before quickly releasing, and marginal contact occurs.
Green (GSW) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Poole (GSW) applies two hands to Crowder's (PHX) back and affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Booker (PHX) applies a hand to the front of Poole (GSW) on the drive and affects his SQBR.
Booker (PHX) dislodges Poole (GSW) from his position as he attempts to secure the ball during the rebound
Thompson (GSW) holds Booker (PHX) during the screen and affects his FOM.
Green (GSW) jumps with the ball in his hands and returns to the floor before releasing the ball for the pass.
Paul gathers the ball in the air, establishing his right foot as his first step, and then makes a legal move to the basket.
Porter Jr. (GSW) applies a stayed forearm to Paul's (PHX) side during the driving shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs.
Craig (PHX) commits a take foul on Green (GSW).
Iguodala (GSW) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Bridges (PHX).
